Reliance Power Gains After Report It Won Five Hydroelectric Power Projects

-- B y   K a r t i k a y   M e h r o t r a
-- 
2011-03-22T03:49:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/reliance-power-gains-after-report-it-won-five-hydroelectric-power-projects.html
Reliance Power Ltd. (RPWR)  gained in
Mumbai trading after the Daily News & Analysis reported the
company won five hydro-power projects totalling 672 megawatts in
the northern state of Himachal Pradesh.  The stock rose 1.5 percent to 120.35 rupees at 9:16 a.m.
local time after climbing as much as 2.1 percent. Reliance Power
spokesman Daljeet Singh declined to comment on the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kartikay Mehrotra in New Delhi at 
 kmehrotra2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
